%description
Header files and runtime libraries for LLVM and Clang. The LLVM Project is a collection of modular and reusable compiler and toolchain technologies. Despite its name, LLVM has little to do with traditional virtual machines. The name 'LLVM' itself is not an acronym; it is the full name of the project.

